description:
Located in a tranquil and well kept block of only 6, this secure three bedroom full brick townhouse offers the ultimate in convenience.

* Well maintained eat-in kitchen with tiled flooring.
* Spacious open plan living area with floorboards.
* Three well-proportioned bedrooms with built-in wardrobes.
* Original bathroom with separate bathtub and shower.
* Private low maintenance courtyard.
* Two balconies on the upper level provide additional outdoor space.
* Second toilet in laundry on lower level.
* Carport over parking space at rear of building.

Location:
* Short walk to Narwee Train Station and buses.
* Easy proximity to John Mountford Reserve and Bennett Park.
* Close to Roselands Shopping Centre and Aquatic Centre.
* Surrounded by numerous schools and childcare centres.
* Easy access to M5 and M8 Motorways.
* Just 18km south-west of the CBD and 14km from Sydney Airport

Outgoings (approximately):
* Strata Levies: $750 per quarter
* Council Rates: $360 per quarter
* Water Rates: $167 per quarter
